has gone above me, you idiot?

356
00:21:26,040 --> 00:21:27,490
Colonel...

357
00:21:27,490 --> 00:21:32,640
Once, I tried putting together a theory 
on how to perform human transmutation.

358
00:21:32,930 --> 00:21:36,800
Just now, I was frantically remembering it.

359
00:21:36,800 --> 00:21:39,900
We alchemists are nasty creatures.

360
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:43,070
If the Elric brothers 
were mixed up in this,

361
00:21:43,070 --> 00:21:45,830
