362
00:21:45,830 --> 00:21:48,820
He didn't have to go 
charging into this alone.

363
00:21:50,280 --> 00:21:52,910
Haven't you figured it out yet?

364
00:21:53,620 --> 00:21:55,340
Figured what out?

365
00:21:55,340 --> 00:21:58,180
When it comes to those brothers,

366
00:21:58,180 --> 00:22:01,280
